```bash
smarttest --system-id 123
```

**Features:**
- ğŸ¨ Color-coded results (green=passed, red=failed, yellow=errors)
- ğŸ“Š Real-time progress bar
- ğŸ“ Results grouped by API endpoint
- ğŸ” Detailed validation failure messages

**Example:**
